  Scenario Outline: Verify launch of registration page
    Given I am a new user
    When I hit the url "<navigatedUrl>"
    Then I should be redirected to the url "<redirectedUrl>"
    
 	Examples:
 	|	navigatedUrl	|	redirectedUrl	|
 	|https://code-stage.whjr.one/trial/register | https://code-stage.whjr.one/coding/mastery/trial/register |
 	|https://code-stage.whjr.one/coding/trial/register	|	https://code-stage.whjr.one/coding/mastery/trial/register?courseType=coding |
  |https://code-stage-byfs.whjr.one/trial/register|https://code-stage-byfs.whjr.one/coding/mastery/trial/register|
  |https://code-stage-byfs.whjr.one/coding/trial/register|https://code-stage-byfs.whjr.one/coding/mastery/trial/register?courseType=coding|
  
  
